# 🎬 MovieVerse - BookMyShow Clone

A full-stack Movie Ticket Booking web application built using **Python, Django, Bootstrap, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.

Users can browse movies, view details, book seats, generate QR code tickets, manage wishlists, and write reviews.

