# ✨ Features

- 🔐 User Authentication (Login & Register)
- 🎬 Browse Movies
- 🔍 Search Movies
- ❤️ Wishlist
- ⭐ Movie Ratings
- 📝 User Reviews
- 🎟 Seat Booking System
- 📅 Show Selection
- 📱 Responsive UI
- 👤 User Profile
- 📜 Booking History
- 📷 QR Code Ticket Generation
- 🌐 Live Deployment

---

# 🛠 Tech Stack

### Frontend

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Bootstrap 5
- JavaScript

### Backend

- Python
- Django

### Database

- SQLite

