---

# ⚙ Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Codeakriti2005/MovieVerse.git
```

Go to project

```bash
cd MovieVerse
```

Create Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

Activate

Windows

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run Server

```bash
python manage.py runserver
```

